Privacy Policy for SQL Query Generator Extension
Introduction
The SQL Query Generator Chrome extension is committed to protecting your privacy. This privacy policy explains how we handle any data in relation to the extension. Our primary focus is ensuring that your data remains private and secure, and we have designed the extension to operate offline without collecting any personal information.

Data Collection and Usage
No Data Collection:

The SQL Query Generator does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data. It functions entirely offline within your browser environment.
Offline Functionality:

All operations and functionalities of the extension are performed locally on your device. There are no connections to external servers or APIs.
Local Data Storage:

Configuration settings, preferences, and any query data are stored locally in your browser's storage. This data is used solely for the purpose of enhancing your experience with the extension.
User Privacy:

We respect your privacy and ensure that no user data is collected or shared with third parties. Your interactions with the extension remain private and secure.
Security
Data Security:
The extension is designed to maintain the integrity and confidentiality of your data by keeping it within your browser. We do not access, collect, or transmit any data outside your device.
Changes to this Privacy Policy
Policy Updates:
We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and we encourage users to review the policy periodically.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, please contact us at befhobby@gmail.com
